Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.01,0:21:04.03,Naslov S,Caption,0,0,0,,{\blur1\bord3\fs70\b1\c&HE04105&\3c&HE8F8F5&\pos(406,545)}Svemirska braća
Dialogue: 1,0:20:49.01,0:21:04.03,Naslov E,EpTitle,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fs52\4c&H3E4242&\fax-0.1\3c&H121E18&\fscx110\pos(701.999,572)}#94 Uzbudljivi\N\h\h\htimski rad
Dialogue: 5,0:20:49.52,0:20:53.38,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\an8}Dok treniramo u pustinji, primetio sam nešto.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:53.38,0:20:56.48,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ova grupa osobenjaka nema vođu.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:56.48,0:20:57.90,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1\an8}Sledeći put, {\i0}Svemirska braća{\i1}:{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:20:58.16,0:20:59.98,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Uzbudljivi timski rad".
Dialogue: 5,0:20:59.98,0:21:03.01,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\an8}U tom slučaju, moraću ja da budem vođa!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.03,0:21:04.03,Default,chapter,0,0,0,,{Mr. Hibbit}
Dialogue: 5,0:21:11.68,0:21:13.45,Default,Fred,0,0,0,,Gosn. Hibit!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:15.96,0:21:17.97,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,Jej!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:21.07,0:21:23.51,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,{\i1}Koristiću ovo da ugasim vatru.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:32.33,0:21:34.35,Default,A,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sistem za gašenje vatre u modulu 5 u kvaru.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:34.62,0:21:36.46,Default,N,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mogućnost eksplozije.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:36.46,0:21:39.34,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,Vatra je prejaka da je ugasi ovaj aparat.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:39.34,0:21:39.98,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,Šta da radim?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:41.32,0:21:43.38,Default,Bud,0,0,0,,Š-Šta sad? Hibit je u nevolji?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:45.00,0:21:45.86,Default,Freddy,0,0,0,,Smirite se.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:46.45,0:21:49.70,Default,Freddy,0,0,0,,Hajde da smislimo način da ugasimo vatru.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:50.19,0:21:52.82,Default,Linda,0,0,0,,Sistem za gašenje vatre ne radi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.20,0:22:00.21,Default,Caption,0,0,0,,{\an8}Modul 5
Dialogue: 5,0:21:53.70,0:22:00.21,Default,Linda,0,0,0,,Da bismo ugasili vatru, moraćemo da izolujemo modul 5 i ugasimo dovod kiseonika bez kojeg ne može da gori.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:00.83,0:22:03.23,Default,Dami,0,0,0,,Nekako sam uspeo da popravim žice.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:03.23,0:22:05.47,Default,Dami,0,0,0,,Iseći ću dotok kiseonika u modul 5.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:05.47,0:22:07.24,Default,Freddy,0,0,0,,Okej, uradi tako.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:07.24,0:22:08.47,Default,Freddy,0,0,0,,{\i1}Čuješ li me, Hibite?
